{"tid":894043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲豬瘟在中國失控　沿路滿是吐血病死豬","createTime":"2018-11-08T05:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T15:25:55.000Z","uid":75969,"like":238,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"f754a5017209799ac21bb854fbe7bdc5e8afdc21","tid":894043,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181108/640_25e18a3ad46a7396290f66ed4c8ed17f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181108%2F640_25e18a3ad46a7396290f66ed4c8ed17f.jpg&h=9f34ca5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n非洲豬瘟在中國蔓延，至今已經有14個省市爆發疫情。中國網路近日流傳一段短片，顯示民眾開車在路上走，但沿路的病死的豬屍，看不出有相關衞生防護，一旁也有居民在散步。<br />\n <br />\n影片沒有標示拍攝的時間和地點，但從畫面可見，路上每隔數公尺就有數隻病死豬的屍體，部分屍體嘴邊還流出大攤血漬。<br />\n <br />\n中國於今年8月發現非洲豬瘟蹤跡，截至上月擴散省市包括遼寧省、黑龍江省、河南省、江蘇省、安徽省、浙江省、內蒙古、吉林省、天津市、山西省、雲南省、湖南省、貴州省等，中國農業農村部昨證實，重慶市酆都縣也發生非洲豬瘟疫情，總計中國已至少有14個省市「淪陷」。有參與防疫的徐姓人員透露，情況「比想像的嚴重」，她認為無論是管理能力或生物技術，中國「無力阻止非洲豬瘟疫情的擴散」。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181108/1462389/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181108%2F1462389%2F&d=Ka4QYMh6GiHTsAA8ISVHEpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=57283b48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181108%2F1462389%2F&h=ebbbacf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181108/1462389/</a>"},{"pid":"325cf7ad39c30d5c19cbac3df1ae4994afff9786","tid":894043,"uid":75969,"like":388,"dislike":2,"score":386,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:57:46.000Z","msg":"唔洗半日班強國人就會搬晒啲死豬返屋企食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d6fb268b6d78064b78972135dc75017bfbd044","tid":894043,"uid":70786,"like":135,"dislike":2,"score":133,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:58:23.000Z","msg":"集中營又多D豬